{"tid":2038562,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國版Steam測試中","createTime":"2020-05-27T15:40:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-27T15:48:33.000Z","uid":134747,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"45da6982a5ae9e441f88bdf7c31166680aa4f88e","tid":2038562,"uid":134747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T15:40:38.000Z","msg":"有中國版steam之稱的「蒸汽平台」在傳出上架日期不遠後，不少玩家便風聲鶴唳，深怕政府當局出手將國際版Steam封鎖。近期，有外國媒體發現蒸汽平台正悄悄進行Alpha版本的測試，並親身體驗了其運作方式。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://根據外媒win.gg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E6%A0%B9%E6%93%9A%E5%A4%96%E5%AA%92win.gg&d=YPabaHIeuUhgFn7y0hV32SrXKCTJ71YGEIw5q99tfRY%3D&h=51f29f07\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">根據外媒win.gg</a>的測試，先前曾報導過的「5秒鐘健康遊戲忠告」於Alpha版本中實裝，提醒玩家適度遊戲，切勿沉迷遊戲外，也呼籲玩家抵制盜版遊戲。<br />\n<br />\n所有新創的帳號名稱皆被預設為一串代碼，大頭貼則是以問號顯示。顯然的，玩家們的帳號名稱及大頭貼似乎皆需要通過「官方」的審查才能正常顯示。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://win.gg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwin.gg&d=YPabaHIeuUhgFn7y0hV32SrXKCTJ71YGEIw5q99tfRY%3D&h=9eb3cf8f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">win.gg</a>的測試人員表示他們在當地下午4點開啟遊戲《絕對武力：全球攻勢》時，照理來說是符合中國政府防沉迷相關法條規定的「晚上10點至早上8點」未成年玩家無法遊玩。但蒸汽平台則是顯示其無法登入，似乎自動套用了中國的時區（當時為凌晨5點）。<br />\n<br />\n上述測試結果也引起了不少中國玩家討論，紛紛表示「現行機制鐵定遭唾棄，玩個遊戲怎一堆限制」、「處處限制還要等遊戲過審，還不一定能過審，傻子才用蒸汽」、「這道牆有點太高，正常玩遊戲太難了」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PTCkWPE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPTCkWPE.jpg&h=c7694610&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mp9CY20.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMp9CY20.jpg&h=1f282a26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WFvVLH0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWFvVLH0.jpg&h=356dbdcc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nsource: <a href=\"https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=749625\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D749625&d=YPabaHIeuUhgFn7y0hV32SrXKCTJ71YGEIw5q99tfRY%3D&h=c343a01f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D749625&h=45794647\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=749625</a>"},{"pid":"7dcb8ee5f73446332c67521788b1e8e56767dc8c","tid":2038562,"uid":30468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T15:43:21.000Z","msg":"會唔會多過5隻遊戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e497a05788cd93537ea301bc4fad1010d104c803","tid":2038562,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T15:44:12.000Z","msg":"由始至終都係濫捕，何來送頭? 你係咪以後唔出街?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2037860\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2037860</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4b8d614e15d9b69ce4b341ba9702386342f51fe0","tid":2038562,"uid":173271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T15:48:33.000Z","msg":"開VPN果d/某地區自動入哂大劣ser可唔可行<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}